ent-CMPosterUNMC = UNMC Poster
    .desc = An old recruitment poster for the UNMC. Looking at it floods you with a mixture of pride and sincere regret.
ent-RMCPosterHorizon = Happy New Horizons Day!
    .desc = An old poster for celebrating the UN New Horizons Day holiday, celebrating hope and rememberance. It features a ship surrounded by stars flying away from a planet.
