ent-CMPosterTartarus = Tartarus Mining co. poster
    .desc = A simplified version of the Tartarus Mining co. logo. The Tartarus Mining Company is owned by Prospectia, a sub-division of the San Rei Corporation, which is in turn owned by the Weston-Yamada Corporation.
