ent-CMPosterSPP3 = Trust In The Strength Of The Union
    .desc = A stylized depiction of the SPP star.
ent-CMPosterSPP4 = Through The Union Our Power Is Secured
    .desc = A stylized depiction of the SPP's flag and the words, 'Our Unity is the dream of all Peoples. Trust in the strength of their Union.'
ent-CMPosterSPP5 = We Forge A Path Into the Stars
    .desc = The head of a man in a SPPAC EVA suit smiles looking not at you, but up to the right of the poster.
ent-CMPosterSPP6 = Our Militaries Secures Our Future
    .desc = A SPPAC Ground Forces soldier stands, rifle at the ready with a defiant and steel-eyed look on his face. The SPP star is in the background.
ent-CMPosterSPP7 = The People's Armed Collective Is Our Backbone
    .desc = SPPAC Ground Forces soldiers, one of whom is a woman and none of whom have a clear race, stare forward stoically.
ent-CMPosterSPP8 = The People's Armed Collective Is Our Backbone
    .desc = SPPAC Ground Forces soldiers, one of whom is a woman and none of whom have a clear race, stare forward stoically. The poster reads, 'The People's Armed Collective represent us all in the sacred war of liberation and defense of the People's Union.
ent-CMPosterSPP9 = Ever Vigilant Against Capitalist Forces
    .desc = A warped screaming eagle made to look like a vulture bears its talons over the SPP homeworld which has the SPP roundel super-imposed over it. The poster reads, 'The UN will not break the resolve of the people.'
ent-CMPosterSPP10 = Ever Vigilant Against The Stooges of Capitalism and Imperialism
    .desc = A decrepit and desiccated, near claw-like hand reaches towards a stylized solar star shaped into the SPP star. The poster reads, 'Even in its death throes, we must remain vigilant of the encroachment of capitalist forces.'
